om the metallic component. Our results indicate that the\nhole-doping-induced insulator-metal transition in Y$_{1-x}$Ca$_x$TiO$_3$ is\nindeed percolative in nature, and thus of inherent first-order character.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 17:28:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-13"}
