s. We find that concentrated breakdown is exhibited by all\nthe three cases near the transition onset and the spot breakdown processes are\nbroadly consistent with the postulates underlying the universal intermittency\ndistribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 14:38:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2021 11:23:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
