id\nvariants, with an acceleration up to factor of 8300 for heterogeneous\nelastic-plastic materials in comparison to the currently fastest available\nsolvers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 15:40:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
